{"tid":2031994,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃之鋒: #國際戰線 突發！超過200位來自23個國家的國會議員發表聯合聲明，表態反對香港國安法！","createTime":"2020-05-23T19:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T03:32:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"950fb1d5b01a00fe2156a92907e5aa992666fb1d","tid":2031994,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T19:28:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/posts/3017478808344607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshuawongchifung%2Fposts%2F3017478808344607&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=d4ba3b1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/posts/3017478808344607</a><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒 Joshua Wong<br />\n19 mins &middot; <br />\n￼#國際戰線 突發！超過200位來自23個國家的國會議員發表聯合聲明，表態反對香港國安法！<br />\n<br />\n在抵抗北京打壓的路上，香港人定必不會孤單，在接下來幾星期不夠的時間，我會與國際戰線手足用盡所有方法爭取國際聲援，在極權與自由的對壘間，希望為香港尋找一線生機￼。￼￼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1264269874576199687\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1264269874576199687&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=54d7d920\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1264269874576199687&h=de90dad2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1264269874576199687</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/97977427_3017475075011647_5252901717774696448_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=7XB8eyNDwyMAX9k71pK&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=d5bbf0e4df36b885c92f2509ef018368&amp;oe=5EEDC5CF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F97977427_3017475075011647_5252901717774696448_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3D7XB8eyNDwyMAX9k71pK%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-